{"tid":2427204,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"呢種男仔係咪好可愛呢？定還是係好痴線呢？","createTime":"2021-02-28T15:30:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-28T21:06:10.000Z","uid":90316,"like":2,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"98e9d6941946c3780b3a7131b0096dc9d059e903","tid":2427204,"uid":90316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T15:30:40.000Z","msg":"如果個男仔畀人拒絕左，個女仔話大家仲可以做朋友。<br />\n<br />\n個男仲未可以move on到，仲成日掛住個女仔。<br />\n<br />\n但佢同個女仔講自己仲未可以好番，可唔可以叫個女仔出嚟食個飯，俾佢發泄下呻下苦水，想講哂佢一直擺係心入面未講嘅嘢，同埋陪多佢一晚，等佢自己可以快啲好番。<br />\n<br />\n咁樣個男仔算唔算幾可愛呢？定還是係好痴線呢？"},{"pid":"24114ab45ff912c30c4922d3663d5503c75153cf","tid":2427204,"uid":56702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T15:31:41.000Z","msg":"Gay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69cc5c886501ebb1f421677cc5eb69703d156d5a","tid":2427204,"uid":192075,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T15:36:51.000Z","msg":"有冇邊一點<br />\n係可以解釋可愛呢兩隻字？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa65a8a80bde2ebc5dca5a75877e4ee0a3bd4348","tid":2427204,"uid":45442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T15:41:49.000Z","msg":"唔會用可愛或者痴線嚟形容佢<br />\n每個人都有佢嘅coping method，佢覺得咁樣work所以有呢個要求，無需要加呢啲標籤俾佢<br />\n<br />\n如果你係嗰個女仔，就睇你係咪真係當佢係朋友<br />\n你朋友有嘢搵你幫忙你又會唔會諗下呢個男仔係可愛定痴線先幫？<br />\n如果你真係當佢係朋友，個要求又係你能力範圍之間，就去幫囉"},{"pid":"48fee00b5197a996671a1abab8b2d0ae84cb0a93","tid":2427204,"uid":57759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T16:10:25.000Z","msg":"On99"},{"pid":"3ffc4d032433ef6d91782123f9875a7b64a65cd5","tid":2427204,"uid":141237,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T16:10:46.000Z","msg":"直程無晒男人既尊嚴，男人老狗，要求個拒絕左你既女仔去安慰返你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n做男人得就得，唔得就消失，諗吓自己點解唔得，點解咁廢，點樣再做好d為下一次做準備，俾d氣概出黎決絕少少，至少都做俾個女仔睇大佬自己都唔好睇落咁軟弱啦。<br />\n<br />\n都做到咁不如喊埋出黎啦，唔爭在"},{"pid":"c65c94a55303559490aae27c6f3606578d635318","tid":2427204,"uid":5700,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T16:12:36.000Z","msg":"咪癲啦ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你咁樣人地憎多你幾錢添呀"},{"pid":"3b40c811a3563df733a99a68434ddec8c5e472ef","tid":2427204,"uid":240150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T16:13:45.000Z","msg":"好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c1b47b06b0b02f3a55a31623e9613467a598ec6","tid":2427204,"uid":258144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T16:18:29.000Z","msg":"咁樣都覺得你可愛即係對你有好感 ＝有機<br />\n如果覺得反感的話都唔會出嚟啦"},{"pid":"ec937083f325fc69ca242efe95c1761363c11b31","tid":2427204,"uid":364397,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T16:26:53.000Z","msg":"咪撚搞禁多野啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你係咪想人地覺得你煩到仆街屌臭你，你先識收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nMove on啦巴打 有咩咪係連登傾囉，一定大把巴絲陪你傾架<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好再死纏個女仔啦，佢再陪多你一日、你都唔會好，只會更加唔捨得、更加難放低"},{"pid":"71461e5dc1ea585fa1bacadbfeba8cf089158391","tid":2427204,"uid":222807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T16:42:36.000Z","msg":"可愛條撚呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"567e3ab2726f28cb794c4e2b9294a8944bffb20b","tid":2427204,"uid":369643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T16:47:46.000Z","msg":"可（能幻 ）愛"},{"pid":"962740c84099cba8cc91fc4ec4071c41b45a7ab3","tid":2427204,"uid":210311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T17:03:33.000Z","msg":"好煩膠好垃圾<br />\n小朋友中學生就得 都柒架啦<br />\n但成年人完全不能接受"},{"pid":"c42284070d525976a1184f4486ccfe2897c20c7c","tid":2427204,"uid":19989,"like":0,"dislik